Package: prematureMortalityCounty
Title: Predictors of Premature Mortality at the US County Level
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("wangyi1010", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A reproducible analysis of the social, behavioural,
    healthcare-access and drug-environment factors associated with premature
    age-adjusted mortality across United States counties, using County Health
    Rankings 2018 and CDC opioid dispensing data. Not a distributable package;
    the DESCRIPTION exists to declare dependencies for renv.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
